sdp/logs/Lead_frac-0113_1777794485.log:2336:sdp/verification/t-009@20260416t043834z-verify.md:8:The implementation successfully adds live performance resource governance as specified. `resource_governor.py` correctly samples CPU pressure, SC node count, sampler load, capture freshness, self-listener RMS, and master bus health. These signals are collapsed into a composite pressure score that drives degradation rules. `duet_composer.py` integrates these rules by shedding optional roles (color, counter-melody) and thinning events (grains, non-accent notes) before affecting primary musical density.
